{"title":"8086汇编入门","uid":"f0c0de9da9f0645c1a8221caa043fe17","slug":"8086汇编入门","date":"2022-05-13T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-21T06:48:13.846Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/8086汇编入门.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220514114805665.png","content":"<h1 id=\"计组回顾\"><a href=\"#计组回顾\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"计组回顾\"></a>计组回顾</h1><h2 id=\"地址线和数据线\"><a href=\"#地址线和数据线\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"地址线和数据线\"></a>地址线和数据线</h2><p>先通过几道题回顾一下CPU的地址总线宽度和数据总线宽度的意义：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>1GB,1MB,1KB分别是（$2^{30}$bit,$2^{20}$bit,$2^{10}&#x3D;1024$bit）。</li>\n<li>一个CPU的寻址能力为8K，那么它的地址总线宽度为（13）。</li>\n<li>8080，8088，80286，80386的地址总线宽度16根，20根，24根，32根，那么它们的寻址能力分别为（$2^{16},2^{20},2^{24},2^{32}$）。</li>\n<li>8080，8088，8086，80286，80386的数据总线宽度8根，8根，16根，16根，32根，则它们一次可以传输的数据为（1B,1B,2B,2B,4B）。</li>\n<li>从内存中读取1024字节的数据，8086至少读取（512）次，80386字少读取（256）次。</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>从上面的题可以看出，地址总线宽度对应CPU的寻址能力，数据总线宽度对应CPU一次能最多够传输的数据（一根数据线传输1bit）。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"存储器\"><a href=\"#存储器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"存储器\"></a>存储器</h2><p>但是，地址线仅仅体现的是CPU的寻址能力，实际的存储单元数还是要看内存的大小：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>1KB的存储器有（1024）个存储单元，编号为（0到1023）。</li>\n<li>1KB的存储器可以存储（$2^{13}$）个bit，（$2^{10}$）个byte。</li>\n<li>在存储器中，数据和指令以（二进制）的形式存放。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"寄存器\"><a href=\"#寄存器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"寄存器\"></a>寄存器</h2><p>CPU由运算器、控制器、寄存器构成。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>运算器进行信息的处理</li>\n<li>控制器控制各种器件的工作</li>\n<li>寄存器进行信息的存储</li>\n<li>CPU内部的总线连接各种器件，进行数据的传送。</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>写汇编代码时，我们需要主要关注CPU中的寄存器。程序员通过改变各种寄存器中的内容来实现对CPU的控制。</p></blockquote>\n<p>不同CPU，寄存器的个数和结构不同。8086CPU的14个寄存器如下：</p>\n<p>AX,BX,CX,DX,SI,DI,SP,BP,IP,CS,SS,DS,ES,PSW。</p>\n<h3 id=\"通用寄存器\"><a href=\"#通用寄存器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"通用寄存器\"></a>通用寄存器</h3><p>F4（AX,BX,CX,DX）是最常用的四个寄存器。它们用于存放一般性的数据，所以称为通用寄存器。且有且仅有它们四个可以分为高八位(H)和低八位(L)。</p>\n<p>16为寄存器最大能存的数据为$2^{16}-1&#x3D;65535$。</p>\n<p>来看几个和寄存器有关的指令：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513160918903.png\" alt=\"image-20220513160918903\"></p>\n<p>指令右边的一般为源操作数，左边的一般为目标操作数或兼源操作数。</p>\n<p>用于寄存器只有16位，所以计算的时候要注意溢出的问题：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513161504341.png\" alt=\"image-20220513161504341\"></p>\n<p>但是，如果我们的操作仅对寄存器的八位进行操作，当低八位溢出的时候，处理方式如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513161756145.png\" alt=\"image-20220513161756145\"></p>\n<p>即AL和AH分开使用时是独立的，AL的溢出不会对AH产生影响。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>要注意指令的两个操作数位数是要相同的，这就是指令对象的一致性。</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"物理地址\"><a href=\"#物理地址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"物理地址\"></a>物理地址</h2><p>CPU访问内存单元时，需要通过地址总线给出内存单元的物理地址。</p>\n<p>所有内存单元构成的存储空间是一个唯一的线性空间，每一个内存单元在这个空间中都有唯一的地址，称这个地址位内存单元的物理地址。</p>\n<p>不同CPU有不同的形成物理地址的方式，以8086为例。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513162705360.png\" alt=\"image-20220513162705360\"></p>\n<p>但是，8086的地址线有20根，寻址能力为$2^{20}$，这就与一次性最多操作16位（CPU内部最多产生16位的地址）产生了矛盾。Intel的做法是将一个地址拆分为段地址和偏移地址：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513163208826.png\" alt=\"image-20220513163208826\"></p>\n<p>这样使用两个寄存器通过地址加法器就可以获得20位的地址了。加法器中的计算规则为：物理地址&#x3D;段地址&lt;&lt;4+偏移地址。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>总结一下就是，CPU访问内存的时候，用一个基础的地址（段地址）和一个相对于基础地址的偏移地址相加，给出内存单元的物理地址。</p>\n<p>可以将段地址&lt;&lt;4看作基础地址。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"段的理解\"><a href=\"#段的理解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"段的理解\"></a>段的理解</h1><p>一般的理解是这样的：我们将（段地址&lt;&lt;4）作为内存的基础地址，根据偏移地址在基础地址的基础上找到真实地址。这样就把内存根据段地址分为多个段，每个段最大为$2^{16}&#x3D;64KB$（16指的是偏移地址的位数，64KB即为其最大值）。</p>\n<p>但是，这个理解是片面的。段只是人为的划分，一个段的长度也不是固定的，而是最大为64KB。段的划分是视情况而定的，不唯一，如：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513165405244.png\" alt=\"image-20220513165405244\"></p>\n<p>一个物理地址可以有多种段地址和偏移地址的组合。</p>\n<h2 id=\"代码段CS和IP\"><a href=\"#代码段CS和IP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码段CS和IP\"></a>代码段CS和IP</h2><p>段地址由段寄存器来装，段地址寄存器有4个：CS、DS、SS、ES。CPU就是通过段寄存器的种类来区分指令和数据的。CS即代码段寄存器，它指定的内存中的二进制串就是指令。</p>\n<p>而偏移地址的存储则是比较复杂的。需要记住：当段寄存器为CS的时候，偏移地址寄存器一定为IP。<code>&lt;mark&gt;</code>CS:IP指向的内容就是当前指令执行的位置。<code>&lt;/mark&gt;</code></p>\n<p>比如，一段程序的执行过程如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513171155911.png\" alt=\"image-20220513171155911\"></p>\n<ol>\n<li>先根据CS和IP定位到当前需要执行的指令的地址，到内存中取出指令，送入指令缓冲器中处理。</li>\n<li>IP加上刚才处理的指令的长度（CISC的不同指令长度不同），然后根据现在的CS和IP取出下一条需要执行的指令。</li>\n<li>……</li>\n</ol>\n<p>但是，处于安全性的考虑，mov是不能改变CS和IP的值的，这时需要jmp指令：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513171937634.png\" alt=\"image-20220513171937634\"></p>\n<p>如果jmp后面只有一个数，那么只改变IP。当然，立即数也可以改成另一个寄存器。</p>\n<h2 id=\"数据段DS\"><a href=\"#数据段DS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"数据段DS\"></a>数据段DS</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>首先要知道8086CPU中一个字就是两个字节，高八位存放高位字节，低八位存放低位字节，所以一个字需要用两个存储单元来存放。对于小端机，低位字节放在低地址单元中，高地址放在高地址单元中。</p></blockquote>\n<p>DS用于存放要访问数据的段地址。</p>\n<p>比如，对于程序：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">mov ds,1000H\nmov al,[0]</code></pre>\n\n<p>首先将数据段的段地址设置为1000H，下一条指令 <code>mov al,[0]</code>是 <code>mov al,ds:[0]</code>的省略，表示将数据段偏移地址为0的数据赋值给al。</p>\n<p>如果[]前给出了具体的寄存器，就以那个寄存器为准；如果缺省则默认为ds。</p>\n<p>知道了这个后，最后再来总结一下mov的操作数：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513185525457.png\" alt=\"image-20220513185525457\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"栈与SS-SP\"><a href=\"#栈与SS-SP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"栈与SS:SP\"></a>栈与SS:SP</h2><h3 id=\"栈的操作\"><a href=\"#栈的操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"栈的操作\"></a>栈的操作</h3><p>8086CPU提供了出栈和入栈的指令，这两个指令都是以一个字作为操作数的，比如只能为ax而不能用ah或al。</p>\n<p><code>push ax</code>表示将寄存器ax中的数据放入栈中，<code>pop ax</code>表示将栈顶数据取出并送入ax中。需要注意入栈和出栈一次操作的都是两个字节。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513190350122.png\" alt=\"image-20220513190350122\"></p>\n<p>内存中的栈是从高地址王低地址增长的，需要注意高位字节需要放到高位地址，低位字节放到低位地址。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220513190455143.png\" alt=\"image-20220513190455143\"></p>\n<p>出栈后，实现了数据的逆序（高位字节和低位字节）</p>\n<h3 id=\"SS与SP\"><a href=\"#SS与SP\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SS与SP\"></a>SS与SP</h3><p>push和pop指令都需要知道当前栈顶的地址。和CS:IP一样，栈通过SS:SP来标志当前的栈顶元素——即任意时刻，SS:SP指向栈顶元素。</p>\n<p>下面分析入栈和出栈SS和SP进行的操作：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>push ax</code>：首先改变sp，使sp&#x3D;sp-2，以当前栈顶作为新的栈顶；然后将ax中的数据送入当前SS:SP指向的地址（栈顶）。</li>\n<li><code>pop ax</code>：和push的顺序相反，先将栈顶的数据送入ax，再使sp+&#x3D;2作为新的栈顶。</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"编写汇编源程序\"><a href=\"#编写汇编源程序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"编写汇编源程序\"></a>编写汇编源程序</h1><p>先要明白几个概念：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>汇编语言</li>\n<li>汇编语言源程序</li>\n<li>汇编程序：将汇编语言翻译为机器语言的目标程序的工具软件，即编译器</li>\n<li>汇编：动词，将汇编语言翻译为机器语言的过程</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"步骤\"><a href=\"#步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"步骤\"></a>步骤</h2><ol>\n<li>使用编辑器编写汇编语言源程序。</li>\n<li>使用masm编译源程序，产生目标文件 <code>.obj</code>文件。</li>\n<li>链接，生成可执行文件。其中可执行文件包含”程序”和”数据”以及相关的描述信息。</li>\n<li>执行可执行文件。因为16位的程序不能在现在的电脑上运行，所以需要用到dosbox。</li>\n<li>调试。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"源程序示例\"><a href=\"#源程序示例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"源程序示例\"></a>源程序示例</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-assembly\" data-language=\"assembly\"><code class=\"language-assembly\">assume cs:codesg\n\ncodesg segment\n\tmov ax,0123H\n\tmov bx,0456H\n\tadd ax,bx\n\n\tmov ax,4c00H\n\tint 21H\ncodesg ends\n\nend</code></pre>\n\n<p>可以把这个程序分为几个部分：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>指令：4~9行的内容，其中8~9行是每个代码段结尾都需要加的，用于标志结尾。int不是整型而是中断的意思。</li>\n<li>伪指令：上面的程序中有三种伪指令 <code>assume</code>、<code>xxx segment……xxx ends</code>、<code>end</code>。<ol>\n<li><code>xxx segment……xxx </code>表示中间的部分为一个段，<code>xxx</code>为标号，用于标识一个段。标号是人为命名的。</li>\n<li><code>assume</code>用于将我们定义的段与段寄存器挂钩。<code>assume</code>就是“令”的意思。</li>\n<li><code>end</code>标志整个程序的结束，一般是 <code>end start</code>。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"实操\"><a href=\"#实操\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实操\"></a>实操</h2><p>现在在dosbox里面来实操运行一下上面的源程序。</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>打开dosbox，将masm编译器所在目录挂载为虚拟磁盘c:盘（A盘、B盘也是可以的）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>编译demo.asm：<code>masm demo.asm</code>，用于不需要lst和crf文件，所以字节回车即可。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220514114409963.png\" alt=\"image-20220514114409963\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>链接，生成可执行文件。用于现在只有 <code>demo.obj</code>做一个文件，所以直接 <code>link demo.obj</code>即可。如果要实现一些高级功能，如输入输出，就还需要链接其他的库。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220514114658226.png\" alt=\"image-20220514114658226\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>直接执行的话什么也看不到，所以通过调试来看程序的运行：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220514114805665.png\" alt=\"image-20220514114805665\"></p>\n<p>每一行输入一个调试命令，t表示执行程序的下一条指令。可以看到，寄存器内容的变化和程序指定的是一样的。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>总结一下整个流程：</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/asm/image-20220514113406482.png\" alt=\"image-20220514113406482\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"reference\"></a>reference</h1>","text":"计组回顾地址线和数据线先通过几道题回顾一下CPU的地址总线宽度和数据总线宽度的意义： 1GB,1MB,1KB分别是（$2^{30}$bit,$2^{20}$bit,$2^{10}&#x3D;1024$bit）。 一个CPU的寻址能力为8K，那么它的地址总线宽度为（13）。 808...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.7k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"兴趣","slug":"兴趣","count":4,"path":"api/categories/兴趣.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"汇编语言","slug":"汇编语言","count":1,"path":"api/tags/汇编语言.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%AE%A1%E7%BB%84%E5%9B%9E%E9%A1%BE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">计组回顾</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E7%BA%BF%E5%92%8C%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BA%BF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">地址线和数据线</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">存储器</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">寄存器</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%AF%84%E5%AD%98%E5%99%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">通用寄存器</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80\"><span class=\"toc-text\">物理地址</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%AE%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%90%86%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">段的理解</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E6%AE%B5CS%E5%92%8CIP\"><span class=\"toc-text\">代码段CS和IP</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%AE%B5DS\"><span class=\"toc-text\">数据段DS</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%88%E4%B8%8ESS-SP\"><span class=\"toc-text\">栈与SS:SP</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A0%88%E7%9A%84%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">栈的操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#SS%E4%B8%8ESP\"><span class=\"toc-text\">SS与SP</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99%E6%B1%87%E7%BC%96%E6%BA%90%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">编写汇编源程序</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">步骤</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%BA%90%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">源程序示例</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E6%93%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实操</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#reference\"><span class=\"toc-text\">reference</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"三维图形程序设计复习","uid":"3fa76c9a07d91a76f2ec71bfcf92406c","slug":"三维图形程序设计复习","date":"2022-05-24T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T13:53:44.786Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/三维图形程序设计复习.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/opengl/review/cover.png","text":"绪论 图形和图像的区别？ 图形由场景的几何模型和景物的物理模型共同组成，更强调场景的几何表示；而图像则是计算机内以位图形式存在的灰度信息。 计算机如何实现三维图形的显示？ 通过透视在2D屏幕上产生3D效果。 通过隐藏面消除、光照和阴影、纹理贴图等增强3D效果。 OpenGL的三种...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"13k","symbolsTime":"12 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"图形学与游戏","slug":"图形学与游戏","count":4,"path":"api/categories/图形学与游戏.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"OpenGL编程","slug":"OpenGL编程","count":3,"path":"api/tags/OpenGL编程.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}}},"next_post":{"title":"js动态解析引入高清B站视频","uid":"04b6f3049f777a677b374cdd0470b88b","slug":"bilibili","date":"2022-05-10T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T13:54:12.419Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/bilibili.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/share/3/cover.png","text":"效果预览首先来看看引入后的效果吧！ var videoObject = { container: '.video', plug:'flv.js', video: 'BV1SE411V78E', }; var player = new ckplayer(videoObject); ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.5k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":14,"path":"api/tags/python.json"},{"name":"bilibili","slug":"bilibili","count":2,"path":"api/tags/bilibili.json"},{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":1,"path":"api/tags/分享.json"},{"name":"闲谈","slug":"闲谈","count":3,"path":"api/tags/闲谈.json"},{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":1,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}}}}